This application simplifies the BIOS, firmware, driver, and application update experience for Dell client hardware.

Name.Display: ASIX USB to Serial/Parallel Port Driver

Description.Display: This package contains the driver for the ASIX serial and parallel port. It fixes the issue where the Bluetooth does not work after the system resumes from hibernation mode.

Name.Display: Intel Gigabit Ethernet Network Controller Driver

Description.Display: This package contains the Intel I2xx and 825xx Gigabit Ethernet Network Controller driver. The Ethernet network driver helps the system to connect to a wired Internet connection.

Name.Display: Qualcomm QCA61x4A QCA9377 WiFi Bluetooth Driver

Description.Display: This package contains the driver for Qualcomm (R) QCA61x4A and QCA9377 Wi-Fi and Bluetooth cards. The package is supported on Dell Tablets and Dell OptiPlex, Latitude, Precision, and XPS systems that run the Windows 10 (64-bit) operating system. The package fixes potential WPA2 vulnerability issue and is Microsoft Windows Redstone 2 (RS2) and Redstone 3 (RS3) signed.

This package contains the driver for Intel HD, 515, 520, 530, 615, 620, 630, P530, P630, Iris 540, and 640 Graphics for 7th and 8th generation Intel processors. A graphics or video driver is the software that enables communication between the graphics card and the operating system, games, and applications.

Description.Display: This package contains the Dell Command | Monitor application. The Dell Command | Monitor software application enables remote management of client systems. It uses application programs to access the system information, monitor the status, or change the state of the system such as remotely shutting down the system.

This package contains the driver for the Intel Management Engine Components Installer. This driver installs Intel Management Engine Interface, Serial Over LAN driver, Local Manageability Service, Intel Converged Security and Manageability Engine (CSME), Windows Management Instrumentation (WMI) provider, Intel Management Security Status application, and Intel Capability Licensing Service Client.
